{"id":544488,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/11/【图说天朝】沧州市第八中学课前宣誓制度及内容/","date":"2016-11-12T07:29:45Z","modified":"2016-11-12T07:29:45Z","title":"【图说天朝】沧州市第八中学课前宣誓制度及内容","content":"<p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1654999207/Eh585s3yb\" target=\"_blank\">@李宝玖</a>：无语了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/62a548a7gw1f9oel47f80j20qo0zk12r.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-544489\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/62a548a7gw1f9oel47f80j20qo0zk12r.jpg\" alt=\"62a548a7gw1f9oel47f80j20qo0zk12r\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/62a548a7gw1f9oel47f80j20qo0zk12r.jpg 960w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/62a548a7gw1f9oel47f80j20qo0zk12r-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/62a548a7gw1f9oel47f80j20qo0zk12r-768x1024.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"WB_text\"><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1819578831\" target=\"_blank\">@独自踌躇</a>：传销组织进校园。<img title=\"[偷笑]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/19/heia_org.gif\" alt=\"[偷笑]\" /></div>\n<blockquote><p>[&#8230;]要求：1、由班长领读，全体起立，手持材料，手臂向前伸。<br />\n2、齐读时声音要洪亮，要有气势，要包含感情，整齐划一，不允许不读。<br />\n3、齐读内容周一至周五每天早晨中午各一次。政教处巡查，纳入量化。齐读内容如下：<br />\n[&#8230;]<br />\n我们，倡导富强、民主、文明、和谐，坚定实现中国梦！<br />\n我们，倡导自由、平等、公正、法治，建设和谐有序新家园！<br />\n我们，倡导爱国、敬业、诚信、友善，提升素质凝聚全民做贡献！</p></blockquote>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,21627],"tags":[10755,13016,24636,11848]}